[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      187[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | **Amazon Neptune** | Stores the formulary knowledge graph; executes openCypher traversals. Use the reader endpoint for query Lambdas, writer endpoint for the loader Lambda. |
[0m[49m[39m  184, 188[0m:[39m[49m | **Amazon S3** | Receives and archives formulary files |
